title: FILMORA VIDEO EDITOR WITH KEY
description:
Note: Wondershare Video Editor is now renamed to Filmora, customers of Video Editor can upgrade for free to check out the latest features! 

Wondershare Filmora, an easy-to-use video editor with all the video editing tools you need, allows you to create Hollywood-like home movies with text, filter, motion and transition effects from all regular videos, audios and photos. Besides, you can directly upload your video to YouTube for sharing with family and friends, save videos for playback on portable devices like iPhone, iPad, iPod, etc. or burn DVD for better video preservation. No matter it's a wedding video, love movie, travel story, life documentary or party record, it is just so easy to turn it to a treasured home video and share it with everyone!
